comment: Booker (BKN) makes marginal contact with Kidd-Gilchrist (CHA) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Kilpatrick (BKN) and gives him room to avoid the contact. Zeller makes marginal contact with his arm.
Zeller (CHA) makes contact across Bogdanovic's (BKN) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Kidd-Gilchrist (CHA) jumps vertically and Zeller (CHA) makes contact with the ball without affecting Kilpatrick's (BKN) shot attempt.
Batum (CHA) holds Bogdanovic (BKN) and affects his movement to retrieve the rebound.
Bogdanovic (BKN) makes contact with Walker (CHA) that affects his SQBR.
Hollis-Jefferson (BKN) makes body to body contact with Walker (CHA) that affects his SQBR.
Zeller (CHA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Kilpatrick (BKN) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Walker (CHA) maintains legal guarding position and does not affect Kilpatrick's (BKN) SQBR.
Lopez (BKN) makes marginal contact to the back of Batum (CHA) and does not affect his movement to retrieve the rebound.
Kidd-Gilchrist (CHA) does not make contact that affects Kilpatrick's (BKN) shot attempt.
Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact with Harris (BKN) on the screen.
